headline: Phillips 66 announces agreement to sell interest in Gulf Coast Express
summary: HOUSTON, December 16, 2024--Phillips 66 announced that it has entered into a definitive agreement to sell DCP GCX Pipeline LLC for pre-tax total cash proceeds of $865 million.

headline: Phillips 66 announces 2025 capital program
summary: HOUSTON, December 16, 2024--Phillips 66 announced a 2025 capital budget of $2.1 billion, including $998 million for sustaining capital and $1.1 billion for growth capital.
